                  java.lang.String passingGrade)
        Creates a reimbursement for the specified employee.
        Parameters:
        em - The employe that submitted the reimbursement.
        description - The description of the reimbursement.
        cost - The cost of the event.
        gradeFormat - The grading format for the event.
        eventType - The event type.
        workJustification - The reason to take the event.
        attachment - An event-related attachement
        approvalDocument - An approval document
        timeMissed - The expected time missed for this event.
        startDate - The start date of the event.
        address - The address of the event.
        city - The city of the event.
        zip - The zip of the event.
        country - The country of the event.
        passingGrade - The passing grade of the event.
        Returns:
        The id of the row that represents the reimbursement.
